Steps to setup autotools for our project:
---------------------------
1. Create src/, build/, m4/, test/ directories
2. Create program file in src
3. Create Makefile.am and write code to build the source files.
4. autoscan and rename configure.scan to configure.ac
5. Edit the configure.ac file according to our project.
6. run ./build-project.sh and generated binary can be found in build/bin.
